text:
This Week in Machine Learning & AI brings you the week’s most interesting and important stories from the world of machine learning and artificial intelligence.

This week’s show explores the White House workshops on AI, human bias in AI and machine learning models, a company working on machine learning for small datasets, plus the latest AI & ML news and a self-driving car that learned how to drive aggressively.

Here are the notes for this week’s stories:
title: The White House on AI & Aggressive Self-Driving Cars — May 27, 2016
